Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.46,0:00:07.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Galactic Imperial Calendar, Year 211
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.79,0:00:07.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time you've been\Nhere, isn't it, Highness?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.30,0:00:11.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard lots of stories about it.\NIt's in textbooks, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.81,0:00:19.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's Rune light!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.20,0:00:29.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is that it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.48,0:00:31.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that's Sakimori Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.61,0:00:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Where our empire began.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.86,0:00:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NAnd a land of curses and blessings.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.02,0:02:26.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inuzuka-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.40,0:02:33.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am...\NWhat am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.89,0:02:45.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not picking up any radio signals.\NTetraxion particle interference?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.50,0:02:50.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Calculating our location based \Non the position of artificial
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.68,0:02:52.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nsatellites, this is the site of an old gravity reactor explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.55,0:02:56.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An area with a radius of 100 km was\Nquarantined as a contaminated zone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.67,0:02:59.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Communications gear unusable.\NNo spare air, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.01,0:03:02.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The conclusion I'm led to is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.93,0:03:06.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What am I thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.85,0:03:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I have\Na reason to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.69,0:03:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Captain Cain of\Nthe Dorssian Lunar Orbital Forces,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}tasked with the extermination of\Nthe Class 7 Special Hazard Organisms.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:31.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We will now tow Module 77\Nto Dorssia Sphere #1.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We finally got our hand \Non one of these things,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.83,0:03:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nso why aren't we allowed to pilot it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.05,0:03:40.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They say that no one but\Nthose students can pilot them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.55,0:03:42.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, that's a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.30,0:03:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I saw Captain Cain piloting one.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.56,0:03:48.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you did?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.15,0:03:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So, this is a Valvrave. I've never\Nseen one up close before.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:59.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say?\NWould you care to try piloting it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I do wish you would relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we are \Nfollowing Council policy
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,of keeping the Magiuses \Na secret, we are friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.33,0:04:13.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.66,0:04:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.66,0:04:23.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is an enemy machine,\Nbut it is a thing of beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Quit screwing around, Sashinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.52,0:04:33.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as we have no proof that you're
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:35.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nhuman, I can't let you aboard this shuttle.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.69,0:04:37.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me that crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.70,0:04:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think Inuzuka-senpai\Nwas trying to prove when he protected you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.78,0:04:46.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I'm grateful to him. But\NI can't accept your whole story yet.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.36,0:04:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You stubborn broad!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.06,0:04:50.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There are a lot of people\Nthat I have to keep safe!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.16,0:04:56.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You betrayed our trust. Do you\Nhave any idea how much Haruto—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:57.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Come on, that's enough!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But she's—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.45,0:05:01.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sashinami made the call that\Nshe had to make as a leader, that's all.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:05.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yamada, did you have\Na better idea at the time?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.14,0:05:09.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have any choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.59,0:05:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can I trust someone who lied to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:24.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This one's no good, either?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.34,0:05:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I can pick up a different\Nsatellite, maybe we can—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.13,0:05:30.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're wasting your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,30 minutes of air left, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.72,0:05:49.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Saki Rukino. You were\Nthere too, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.98,0:05:52.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The person who shot\Nmy eye out was...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.27,0:06:01.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly as you imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:05.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The L-elf who shot out your eye\Nwas body-jacked at the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.70,0:06:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought.\NL-elf, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.18,0:06:15.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This country has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.36,0:06:18.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The Dorssia Military\NPact Federation...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.79,0:06:21.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Initially, it was an organization \Ndedicated to military mutual
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.85,0:06:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,assistance meant to stand up \Nto more developed countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.38,0:06:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But now, it's a political power \Nplayer that pursues interests
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.01,0:06:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and power just as much as \NARUS. No, even more so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.10,0:06:34.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A former prince certainly has\Na higher perspective on such matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.43,0:06:36.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is not because I am royalty\Nthat I am lamenting that fact.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.39,0:06:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It is because I am\Na Dorssian citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.03,0:06:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That, L-elf, is why I am gathering power\Nwith the intent of liberating Dorssia.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.20,0:06:56.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know full well that it is\Na grandiose dream. Nevertheless...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.38,0:06:59.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not that, A-drei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.19,0:07:04.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm laughing because\NI plan to liberate it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.94,0:07:10.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was the one who lost faith.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.69,0:07:29.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf. I found a signal flare!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.61,0:07:34.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can repair it, can't you?\NWe can use this to call for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.53,0:07:37.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible. Not without\Na piezoelectric fuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.63,0:07:42.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want to be rescued?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.81,0:07:45.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you trying to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.34,0:07:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Because all our schoolmates \Nare in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\NWe have to get back there right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.76,0:07:50.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're still spewing that nonsense?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.96,0:07:52.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've been abandoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.01,0:07:54.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,By even Shoko Sashinami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.43,0:07:59.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The only ones who eat humans are\Nyou and the other monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't touch me, you liar!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.29,0:08:06.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All this time...\NYou've been lying to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.82,0:08:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.82,0:08:12.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It... it was because\NShoko's the prime minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:13.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:15.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Learn when to give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:19.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto Tokishima. There's no\Ngoing back to the way things were.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:21.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You are a monster!\NAn enemy of humanity!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.67,0:08:22.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.42,0:08:23.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the enemy of\NShoko Sashinami!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.63,0:08:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.59,0:08:27.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How am I wrong?\NFace reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:31.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones\Nwho created that reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This all happened\Nbecause you attacked us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.18,0:08:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't try to shift the blame!\NEvery choice was made by you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.10,0:08:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.35,0:08:40.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All I do is lose people\Nthat are precious to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.90,0:08:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Inuzuka-senpai,\NMarie, even Aina-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.77,0:08:48.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All because...\NAll because of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.07,0:08:52.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the only one who\Nlost someone! I lost Lieselotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.95,0:08:57.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think for a minute \Nthat you're the only one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:09:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who's allowed to dream of a future!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:06.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a shot with her now.\NYou killed Shoko Sashinami's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.54,0:09:09.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,In the battle before we \Narrived in lunar orbit,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nyou annihilated the enemy's fleet, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.05,0:09:15.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shoko Sashinami's father was\Naboard one of the ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.92,0:09:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why didn't you tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.73,0:09:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What good would it have done?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.14,0:09:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You only would have \Ntortured yourself over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.40,0:09:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give up on her. It's impossible\Nto repair that relationship.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.37,0:09:35.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Not for someone who's a monster\Nand her father's killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.41,0:09:40.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.16,0:09:44.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without the Valvrave,\Nyou can't possibly beat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.10,0:10:04.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yamada, if the Allied Forces attack,\Nwill you still defend
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.48,0:10:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sashinami and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.19,0:10:08.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I ain't gonna act like \NI ain't the kind of guy
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nwho picks and chooses who he helps.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.43,0:10:16.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't that right, Inuzuka-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.21,0:10:28.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is apple okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:30.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.38,0:10:34.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay. If you're\Nhungry, just say so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.67,0:10:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Shoko... Did we\Ndo something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.12,0:10:45.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What did we do\Nthat was so bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.50,0:10:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. We didn't do\Nanything wrong at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.11,0:10:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.55,0:11:16.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to let\Nthe Valvraves sit idle.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.34,0:11:20.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto isn't coming back.\NSo that means I...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.72,0:11:28.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"Do you resign as a human being?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.02,0:11:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and press "Yes"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.10,0:11:34.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto isn't piloting me, so I'm hungry!\NStarving, starving, starving!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:35.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.14,0:11:38.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto pressed the "Yes" button?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He wanted revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.19,0:11:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,He said he wanted to get revenge.\NFor someone named Shi... Shoko, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.58,0:11:51.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Give up my humanity?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:55.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. This won't\Nwork if you're still human.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.58,0:11:58.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What won't work?\NThe Valvraves?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:12:03.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Where did I put it?\NIt was on the first day, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.85,0:12:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.93,0:12:12.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Work! Work! You're\Na weapon, aren't you?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.69,0:12:16.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to avenge Shoko! Please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.23,0:12:19.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto, you didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.63,0:12:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You did it for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.12,0:12:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don't do this! I won't\Nlet you touch the Valvraves!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:38.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.27,0:12:54.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You've gotten on my nerves\Nfrom the day I first met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're always looking\Ndown on everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.27,0:13:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You and your "halfsies"!\NYou talk just like Lieselotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.00,0:13:07.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're so smart, why did\Nwe get into this mess?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:11.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If I'd had a Valvrave,\NI would have saved Lieselotte!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.02,0:13:13.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:16.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you so desperately\Ntrying to survive for?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.77,0:13:20.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your survival means\Nthe devouring of many human lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.46,0:13:23.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you insist on spouting \Nidealistic crap about wanting to
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.21,0:13:26.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,save others, die here so you \Nwon't cause any more suffering!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:33.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Your princess was\Na "monster" just like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:34.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.10,0:13:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lieselotte was a Magius.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.56,0:13:37.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What a pathetic lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.80,0:13:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she were a Magius,\Nshe wouldn't have been held prisoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.23,0:13:41.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She had sided with humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she had a falling \Nout with the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.03,0:13:45.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Council?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.24,0:13:48.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,An organization that keeps the existence of\NMagiuses secret from the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.83,0:13:50.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Preposterous.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.04,0:13:52.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Could an individual \Nhave built the Phantoms
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.70,0:13:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand gotten the UN to take action?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.14,0:13:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The girl you fell in love with\Nwas a Magius.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.42,0:13:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:03.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She was ageless, had lived \Nfar longer than you,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.36,0:14:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nand was a monster who fed on human life force!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.68,0:14:07.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.97,0:14:10.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!\NShut up! Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.51,0:14:11.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Shut your mouth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:31.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lieselotte, I can't believe\Nthat you were a Magius...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.28,0:14:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}An ageless being who had\Nlived for centuries.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:41.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The top of the food chain.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.64,0:14:47.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe I had been\Ntrying to save someone like you.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.76,0:14:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What a joke!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.43,0:14:54.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Tears...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, right... It's because\NI made him sad...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And not just L-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:04.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that why I'm being punished?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.62,0:15:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think you've\Ndone enough, Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.75,0:15:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.04,0:15:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you've done\Nmore than enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay to finally rest,\Ndon't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.16,0:15:24.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That world is nothing\Nbut suffering, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.48,0:15:29.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Have I done all I could?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.05,0:15:33.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You put up a good fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.14,0:15:35.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.01,0:15:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that I wanted \Nto hear someone say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.00,0:15:57.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had it all wrong, thinking\Nyou were being held prisoner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because you were\None of them all along!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.03,0:16:11.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She had sided with humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:14.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why she had a falling \Nout with the Council.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.88,0:16:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're wrong. Lieselotte really\Nwas being held prisoner.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:25.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What reason could she have had\Nfor siding with humanity?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.52,0:16:28.88,Italics,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The only clue is Lieselotte's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.50,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Her actions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:33.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She worked with the Royalists\Nand assisted us.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.00,0:16:37.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough.\NI'm just going to pack it in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.41,0:16:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're dying for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:43.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You gave it everything you had, even\Nbecoming a Kamitsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was all for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.39,0:16:46.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.61,0:16:49.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So what was I even\Nborn for, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.76,0:16:54.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To have my body tinkered with\Nand be used as a lab rat?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.20,0:16:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.55,0:16:58.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To pilot a Valvrave?\NTo kill people?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.29,0:16:59.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.81,0:17:02.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.35,0:17:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why did Lieselotte, who had \Nprobably lived for centuries as
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.94,0:17:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a Magius, side with humanity?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.11,0:17:12.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What happened to you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.86,0:17:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Michael...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are very young, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.21,0:17:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But there is no path\Nahead of us to travel down yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.75,0:17:35.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, were you trying to\Ncreate a path?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.81,0:17:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For both human and Magius?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.51,0:17:43.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,My Runes are almost gone.\NI'm out of time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's exactly why. Let's at least\Ngo out kicking and screaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.60,0:17:52.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is something left\Nthat you can do, isn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't spend my life with you anymore.\NBut I can carry on your dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.38,0:18:03.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When I was prepared\Nto die, I felt free.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:06.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what\Nanyone else thinks of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:09.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What matters is\Nwhat I want to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.17,0:18:11.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.91,0:18:13.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...I can't die yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.59,0:18:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.53,0:18:23.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.52,0:18:26.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.15,0:18:32.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto Tokishima,\Nwhat was that just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.64,0:18:35.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\NBut that light, it was...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.36,0:18:38.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it looked just\Nlike Cain's light.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.81,0:18:41.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,True, it should come as no surprise that a Kamitsuki\N
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,would be capable of the \Nsame feats as a Magius...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.16,0:18:47.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf. Do you think we can use\Nthis power to save ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:51.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It might be able to ignite\Nthe signal flare you found!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.88,0:18:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf. I really do care \Nabout everyone at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.10,0:18:58.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to laugh with them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.83,0:19:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll build a place where human\Nand Kamitsuki can live together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.50,0:19:05.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. This time, it won't\Nbe a replacement for JIOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.56,0:19:09.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We'll create a country\Nfor us and by us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.25,0:19:14.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The light that Cain produced\Nwas probably Runes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:17.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The key to triggering them is\Ninformation in the form of speech.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.86,0:19:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like a magic spell?\NBut I don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.96,0:19:22.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You spoke words that were\Nclose to being a spell.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:26.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't perfect, but they were\Nwords close enough to trigger it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.41,0:19:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we send up a signal flare,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.10,0:19:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it doesn't mean it will be \Nan ally who comes for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.21,0:19:37.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a gamble.\NOne with rather poor odds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.58,0:19:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But they aren't zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:43.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf. Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.35,0:19:44.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:46.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As I said, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.68,0:19:47.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,...can't die yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.15,0:20:09.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A world where human and\NKamitsuki can live together, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be a long fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:13.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.65,0:20:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You have an idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.87,0:20:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.65,0:20:16.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.84,0:20:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that we'll all\Nthink of something together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The students, you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.53,0:20:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The whole world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.42,0:20:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To do that, they have to know about\Nthe Magiuses and the Council of 101.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.49,0:20:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I follow you. Expose the truth of\Nthe world, in other words.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.65,0:20:35.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiding the truth caused\Nnothing but misery.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.37,0:20:37.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.59,0:20:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:41.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing else that\Nyou're hiding from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.32,0:20:44.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There is.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.02,0:20:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.88,0:20:52.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.21,0:20:54.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.30,0:21:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Class 7 Special Hazard Organism\Nand deserter located!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.24,0:21:08.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Will now exterminate in accordance with\NUN Harmful Organism Control Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.84,0:21:13.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From beginning to end,\Nwe were a terrible team.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.93,0:21:16.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're polar opposites.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.33,0:21:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Unit 4?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.58,0:21:31.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Rukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto! L-elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.59,0:21:38.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I found you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.17,0:21:45.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a Class 7 Special Hazard\NOrganism! Shoot it down!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:53.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Haruto Tokishima.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.60,0:21:57.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's forge a new pact.\NTo expose the truth of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.75,0:22:01.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, L-elf.\NThis isn't a pact.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.45,0:22:06.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.20,0:22:31.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,L-elf, H-neun, and now you...\NWhat on earth is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't a betrayal.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.57,0:22:39.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This is punishment\Ndirected at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.34,0:24:19.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, episode 23.\N"The Operation to Retake Module 77."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.83,0:24:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Valvrave the Liberator...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.82,0:24:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.82,0:24:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The system that will expose \Nthe truth of the world.